con:soapui-project.name: PurposeForOfUse_Passthrough_CommunityConfig
con:soapui-project.con:description:
Before executing the test suites/cases, make sure the gateway is in passthru mode.
Execute the SetAllServicesToPassthru from the ChangeMode project to set the gateway in passthru mode or restart the app server in passthru mode.
The test should be performed at test suite level as the set up scripts are set up in test suite level. If specific test cases are executed, the result may not be correct.

con:testSuite.name: Passthrough_g1_community_True_2.2true
con:testSuite.con:description:
Testing for Purpose Of/For Use. This suite sends a request message to the g1 entity interfaces, with the Community spring proxy, purposeForUseEnabled=true in gateway.properties, and 2.2=true in purposeUse.properties. Because this is a g1 test suite, all spec versions are 2011. Messages to 2011 specs do not respect the Purpose Of/For Use settings, and thus PurposeOfUse should be used.
Before executing the test suites/cases, make sure the gateway is in passthru mode.
Execute the SetAllServicesToPassthru from the ChangeMode project to set the gateway in passthru mode or restart the app server in passthru mode.

con:testSuite.name: Passthrough_g0_community_True_2.2true
con:testSuite.con:description:
Testing for Purpose Of/For Use. This suite sends a request message to the g0 entity interfaces, with the Community spring proxy, purposeForUseEnabled=true in gateway.properties, and 2.2=true in purposeUse.properties. Because this is a g0 test suite, all spec versions are 2010. Messages to 2010 specs respect the Purpose Of/For Use settings, and thus PurposeForUse should be used.
Before executing this test suites, make sure the gateway is in passthru mode.
Execute the SetAllServicesToPassthru from the ChangeMode project to set the gateway in passthru mode or restart the app server in passthru mode.

con:testSuite.name: Passthrough_g1_community_False_2.2true
con:testSuite.con:description:
Testing for Purpose Of/For Use. This suite sends a request message to the g1 entity interfaces, with the Community spring proxy, purposeForUseEnabled=false in gateway.properties, and 2.2=true in purposeUse.properties. Because this is a g1 test suite, all spec versions are 2011. Messages to 2011 specs do not respect the Purpose Of/For Use settings, and thus PurposeOfUse should be used.
Before executing this test suites, make sure the gateway is in passthru mode.
Execute the SetAllServicesToPassthru from the ChangeMode project to set the gateway in passthru mode or restart the app server in passthru mode.

con:testSuite.name: Passthrough_g0_community_False_2.2true
con:testSuite.con:description:
Testing for Purpose Of/For Use. This suite sends a request message to the g0 entity interfaces, with the Community spring proxy, purposeForUseEnabled=false in gateway.properties, and 2.2=true in purposeUse.properties. Because this is a g0 test suite, all spec versions are 2010. Messages to 2010 specs respect the Purpose Of/For Use settings, and thus PurposeForUse should be used.
Before executing this test suites, make sure the gateway is in passthru mode.
Execute the SetAllServicesToPassthru from the ChangeMode project to set the gateway in passthru mode or restart the app server in passthru mode.

con:testSuite.name: Passthrough_g1_community_True_2.2false
con:testSuite.con:description:
Testing for Purpose Of/For Use. This suite sends a request message to the g1 entity interfaces, with the Community spring proxy, purposeForUseEnabled=true in gateway.properties, and 2.2=false in purposeUse.properties. Because this is a g1 test suite, all spec versions are 2011. Messages to 2011 specs do not respect the Purpose Of/For Use settings, and thus PurposeOfUse should be used.
Before executing this test suites, make sure the gateway is in passthru mode.
Execute the SetAllServicesToPassthru from the ChangeMode project to set the gateway in passthru mode or restart the app server in passthru mode.

con:testSuite.name: Passthrough_g0_community_True_2.2false
con:testSuite.con:description:
Testing for Purpose Of/For Use. This suite sends a request message to the g0 entity interfaces, with the Community spring proxy, purposeForUseEnabled=true in gateway.properties, and 2.2=false in purposeUse.properties. Because this is a g0 test suite, all spec versions are 2010. Messages to 2010 specs respect the Purpose Of/For Use settings, and thus PurposeForUse should be used.
Before executing this test suites, make sure the gateway is in passthru mode.
Execute the SetAllServicesToPassthru from the ChangeMode project to set the gateway in passthru mode or restart the app server in passthru mode.

con:testSuite.name: Passthrough_g1_community_False_2.2false
con:testSuite.con:description:
Testing for Purpose Of/For Use. This suite sends a request message to the g1 entity interfaces, with the Community spring proxy, purposeForUseEnabled=false in gateway.properties, and 2.2=false in purposeUse.properties. Because this is a g1 test suite, all spec versions are 2011. Messages to 2011 specs do not respect the Purpose Of/For Use settings, and thus PurposeOfUse should be used.
Before executing this test suites, make sure the gateway is in passthru mode.
Execute the SetAllServicesToPassthru from the ChangeMode project to set the gateway in passthru mode or restart the app server in passthru mode.

con:testSuite.name: Passthrough_g0_community_False_2.2false
con:testSuite.con:description:
Testing for Purpose Of/For Use. This suite sends a request message to the g0 entity interfaces, with the Community spring proxy, purposeForUseEnabled=false in gateway.properties, and 2.2=false in purposeUse.properties. Because this is a g0 test suite, all spec versions are 2010. Messages to 2010 specs respect the Purpose Of/For Use settings, and thus PurposeOfUse should be used.
Before executing this test suites, make sure the gateway is in passthru mode.
Execute the SetAllServicesToPassthru from the ChangeMode project to set the gateway in passthru mode or restart the app server in passthru mode.
